task.summary: - Added lead list and lead creation logic&view - Some refactoring for better angular minification
- Removed unwanted dependencies - Translated logout button
- Fancy alerts for user administration - Added OwnerId field

- Moved api url to $rootScope variable - Fixed issue with invalid checkbox checking in user editModal.html - App now is in /frontend/ on production and this dir is not shown to user, so made some magic to hide it - Added date column in lead list - Name, patronymic and last name are just one field - Added ftp upload task to gruntfile - Fixed navbar markup to be shown good on mobiles
- Removed sample lead data and sample admin login - Removed user_id sending for lead list
- Added user_id passing to server depending on request method
